    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const d = $input.first().json;\n\nreturn [{\n  json: {\n    to: d.contactEmail,\n    subject: `Quick check-in — ${d.clientName}`,\n    html: `<p>Hi ${d.contactFirstName || 'there'},</p><p>Just wanted to check in and make sure everything is running smoothly on your end. It's been a bit since we last connected.</p><p>Is there anything you need from us? Any questions about the systems we've built? Any new processes you'd like to automate?</p><p>Happy to jump on a quick call anytime: ${d.config.owner.calendarLink}</p><p>— John<br/>${d.config.owner.companyName}</p>`,\n    workflowName: 'SYS 05 — Client Health Monitoring'\n  }\n}];"
      },
